snippet.title: Wreckfest - Teaser Trailer | PS5
snippet.description:
More speed. More power. More mayhem. Wreckfest is coming to PlayStation 5 on June 1st, 2021.

Experience carnage in 4K at a smooth 60 frames per second, wreck online with up to 24 players, and crash in style with enhanced visuals, including dynamic dirt, better textures and improved visual effects.
---
Website: https://order.wreckfestgame.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/wreckfest

#Wreckfest #DriveHardDieLast
